data.description: Discover this captivating ranch-style home, featuring 4 cozy bedrooms and 3 well-appointed full baths, situated in a highly sought-after location with easy access to amenities and transport links. The residence showcases an efficient layout, optimizing space and flow, complemented by rich hardwood floors that exude a sense of warmth and elegance. The expansive yard, ideal for leisure or hosting gatherings, is enhanced by a welcoming back deck. Additionally, a sizable storage shed provides generous space for organization and hobbies. This home is a perfect fusion of comfort and practicality, set in a location that promises convenience and ease of living. USDA eligible!
